 style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;"><span style="color:#003965;"><span style="font-family:symbol;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;">·</span></span></span><span style="color:#003965;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;">  Retaining </span></span></span><span style="color:#003965;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;">structure</span></span></span><span style="color:#003965;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;">s </span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;"><span style="color:#003965;"><span style="font-family:symbol;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;">·</span></span></span><span style="color:#003965;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;">  Introduction to Eurocodes </span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;"><span style="color:#003965;"><span style="font-family:symbol;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;">·</span></span></span><span style="color:#003965;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;">  Sustainability: an introduction to the role of geotechnical engineering in delivering sustainability. </span></span></span></p></div>',
